Package: ConsensusPeaks
Title: A Method for Peak Merging And Distribution Fitting Across Biological Replicates
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Helen", "Zhu", email = "helen.zhu@mail.utoronto.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"), person("Stefan", "Eng", email = "stefaneng13@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: A method for merging peaks called across biological replicates, in bed file format, and modelling the density functions of the resulting distributions.
